<p>将mysql/lib/libmysqlclient.so.18.1.0库文件拷贝到/lib64下，拷贝后命名为libmysqlclient.so.16
[root@test-huanqiu~]# cp /usr/local/mysql/lib/libmysqlclient.so.18.1.0 /lib64/libmysqlclient.so.16</p>

<p>[root@test-huanqiu~]# cat /etc/ld.so.conf
include ld.so.conf.d/*.conf
/usr/local/mysql/lib/
/lib64/
[root@test-huanqiu~]# ldconfig</p>

<p>最后卸载perl-DBD-MySQL，并重新安装perl-DBD-MySQL
[root@test-huanqiu~]# rpm -qa|grep perl-DBD-MySQL
